basicInfo.name: Rosie
basicInfo.flavor: Rosie is unable to break free from the spirits of those she killed in the past. She decides to abandon her name and title, and enters a monastery to redeem herself.

Normal Attack.desc:
2 Enemies
 - Deals damage equal to 30% of Magic Attack plus 7% of the caster's Max HP 1 time(s).
 - 100% chance to inflict Effect Resist Reduction. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Adds Effect: 100% chance to inflict 16% Effect Resist Reduction. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]

Skill 1.name: Judgment of Moonlight
Skill 1.desc:
All Enemies
 - Deals damage equal to 30% of Magic Attack plus 7% of the caster's Max HP 2 time(s).
 - 25% chance to inflict Death. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Damage: To 37% of Magic Attack plus 10% of the caster's Max HP.
 - Increases Chance: Death chance becomes 35%.

Skill 2.name: Holy Prayer
Skill 2.desc:
2 Allies
 - Revives fallen target(s) with 40% HP.
 - Grants Guts upon revival. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
 - All Enemies
 - 100% chance to inflict Buff Duration Reduction. [Reduced by: 2 Turn(s)]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Effect: HP gained upon revival becomes 55%.
 - 2 Allies
 - Adds Effect: Guts upon revival. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)]
Transcend Lv.6 Effect
 - Changes Number of Targets: To All Allies

Passive.name: Blessing of the Dead
Passive.desc:
Self
 - Grants Max HP-Based Defense Boost. [Always Active]
 - Grants All Damage Immunity when HP falls to 50% or lower. [Duration: 2 Turn(s)] [Once per Battle]
 - Grants All Damage Immunity when HP falls to 50% or lower. [Duration: 3 Turn(s)] [Once per Battle]
 - Allies (Defense and Universal)
 - Grants Effect Probability Boost. [Always Active]
Skill Enhancement Effect
 - Increases Turns: All Damage Immunity duration becomes 3 turn(s).
Transcend Lv.2 Effect
 - Increases Effect: Effect Probability Boost to 26%.
